cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.MM

The paper deals with the optimization of a constellation for satellite communications, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The use of genetic algorithms for optimization is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the optimization of the constellation can also have applications in multimedia systems (cs.MM).
